translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  8,46,"Kananjalo thobelani uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe, ningaphikisani, hleze nityhafe nimkelwe nangamandla, yibani nomonde. Inene uAllâh Unabo banomonde (banyamezelayo)"
  8,47,"Ningabi njengabo baphuma emizini yabo beqhayisa khon’ukuze babonwe ngabantu, bathintele abantu bangangeni eNdleleni ka-Allâh; ukanti uAllâh nguMrhangqeli wako konke oko bakwenzayo"
  8,48,"Yabonani uShaytân wenza izenzo zabo ezingcolileyo zaba ngathi zilungile kubo wathi kubo: “Akukho mntu ebantwini onokunoyisa nina namhlanje. Yaye mna ndingummelwane wenu (ndiya kuba nani ndinincedise).” Kodwa yathi yakujamelana imikhosi yomibini, wabaleka wemka yena esithi: “Inene mna andinanto yakwenza nani. Inene mna ndibona eningakuboniyo nina. Inene mna ndiyamoyika uAllâh kuba uAllâh Ubuhlungu esohlwayweni”"
  8,49,"Kekalokuabahanahanisibekunyenabobanesifoezintliziyweni zabo, bathi: “Aba bantu (amaMuslim) bakhohliswe yinkolo yabo.” Kodwa\tlowo\tubeka\tithemba\tlakhe\tkuAllâh,\tuAllâh, nguSomandla, nguSobulumko"
  8,50,"Ukuba unokukhe ubukele xa iingelosi zikhupha imiphefumlo kwabo bangakholwayo (xa besifa); zibabetha ebusweni babo nasemiqolo yabo, (zisithi): “Ngcamlani ke isohlwayo soMlilo odwanguzayo.”"
  8,51,"“Oku kungenxa yoko kwenziwa zizandla zenu, inene uAllâh AkangoMsweli bulungisa kwizicaka zaKhe"
  8,52,"Njengesimilo sabantu bakwaFir’awn, nabo bangaphambili kubo, bazala iiVesi zika-Allâh, Wabohlwaya ke uAllâh ngezono zabo. Inene uAllâh, nguSomandla, Ubuhlungu esohlwayweni"